description: Stunning contemporary penthouse duplex with corner exposure! This spacious penthouse duplex offers abundant natural light, featuring a grand living/dining area with oversized windows, 10-ft ceilings, and a gas fireplace. The chef’s kitchen boasts custom European cabinetry, white Silestone countertops, a vented stainless steel cooktop, convection wall oven, and ample storage. A welcoming entryway includes extra storage and a powder room, with dark-stained oak flooring throughout. Upstairs are two ensuite bedrooms, a full laundry room with sink and cabinetry, a dedicated study area and custom built-in Italian wardrobes. The property includes a full garage parking space with additional storage. Enjoy sweeping city views from your private roof deck. Ideal location just a short distance to the Seaport, Fort Point and downtown Boston.
